videos.headline: Horston fends off the contact for and-1
videos.description: Tennessee's Jordan Horston gets the ball, splits the defense and drains the bucket while drawing the foul.

videos.headline: Burrell accidentally takes out cheerleader after and-1
videos.description: Rae Burrell drives in and sinks the bucket while drawing the foul. While walking backward, she accidentally knocks over a cheerleader.
